      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I already tried taking a break. I took a week off last month and it didn't help at all. The dread just comes back the second I wake up. It’s not just being tired like I need sleep, it's this deep, heavy feeling that the whole thing is just... broken. Like even if I succeed now, it won't fix the fact that I've lost everything while trying to get here. It feels like I'm just stuck in a loop of suffering.",
